comments: Rozier (CHA) is turning away from Green (HOU) when marginal contact occurs with Green's right foot and front as he leans forward toward Rozier during his upward shooting motion.

Tate (HOU) and McDaniels (CHA) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each pursue the rebound. Tate and McDaniels then make incidental leg-to-leg contact as they each return to the floor.
Tate (HOU) moves forward with his left hand brought toward Rozier's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs with Rozier's front as he accelerates toward the wing.
Tate (HOU) brings his left hand toward Rozier's (CHA) front and marginal contact occurs prior to Rozier releasing the pass.
Martin Jr. (HOU) is turning alongside McDaniels' (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs with McDaniels' front/side as he drives into the lane.
Martin Jr. (HOU) brushes McDaniels' (CHA) right leg and marginal contact occurs during McDaniels' jump shot attempt.
Matin Jr.'s (HOU) left arm comes down slightly and marginal contact occurs with Plumlee's (CHA) left arm as Plumlee elevates for the layup attempt.
Smith Jr. (CHA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Green (HOU) as simultaneous incidental body contact occurs.
Smith Jr. (CHA) moves somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with Green (HOU) during the drive.
Green (HOU) releases his off-arm away from Smith Jr.'s (CHA) front and marginal contact occurs as Green steps back toward the corner.
Plumlee (CHA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Smith Jr. (CHA) legally contests Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) commits a take foul on Washington (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) legally contests Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) brushes Rozier's (CHA) left arm and marginal contact occurs prior to Rozier starting his dribble.
Rozier (CHA) grasps and then quickly releases Green's (HOU) shorts. Rozier and Green then make incidental foot-to-foot contact as Rozier dribbles toward half-court.
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on Smith Jr. (CHA).
McDaniels (CHA) and Green (HOU) come together at the same spot inside half-court and marginal contact occurs as McDaniels slows his momentum.
Tate (HOU) and Green (HOU) double team McDaniels (CHA) along the sideline and marginal body contact occurs prior to McDaniels releasing the pass.
McDaniels' (CHA) pass attempt stays in bounds and does not make contact with the sideline.
Sengun (HOU) commits a take foul on Plumlee (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) moves laterally into Green (HOU) and initiates body contact that affects Green's SQBR. The contact occurs prior to the start of Green's upward shooting motion.
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on McGowens (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) and Washington (CHA) legally contest Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Tate (HOU) grasps and then quickly releases Plumlee's (CHA) arm during rebounding.
